  "markup": "\u003Cp style=\u0022mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;\u0022 class=\u0022MsoNormal\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none;\u0022\u003EShould you require an extended period of time off for personal reasons not covered by other leave policies (such as FMLA, sick leave, or vacation), you may request a Personal Leave of Absence. These leaves are typically unpaid and granted at our discretion, based on business needs and your circumstances. This policy outlines the eligibility criteria, the application and approval process, and the potential impact on your benefits and employment status during a personal leave.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;\u0022 class=\u0022MsoNormal\u0022\u003E\u0026nbsp;\u003C/p\u003E"
